{"text_id":164896,"tokens":["The"," virtual"," landscape"," has"," extensively"," redefined"," the"," educational"," system",","," particularly"," through"," online"," classes"," and"," video"," conferences","."," However",","," these"," technological"," advancements"," are"," not"," without"," drawbacks","."," It"," is"," undeniable"," that"," while"," some"," argue"," in"," favor"," of"," flexibility"," and"," accessibility",","," the"," negative"," consequences"," on"," students","\u2019"," social"," life",","," quality"," of"," one","-","on","-","one"," instruction",","," and"," increased"," screen"," time"," make"," a"," strong"," case"," against"," schools"," offering"," such"," options",".","\n","Pri","marily",","," the"," social"," aspect"," of"," learning"," is"," drastically"," diminished"," in"," an"," online"," setting","."," Traditional"," classroom"," environments"," naturally"," foster"," social"," skills"," through"," peer"," interaction"," and"," collaborative"," learning"," experiences","."," Engaging"," in"," debates",","," group"," work",","," and"," even"," the"," simple"," conversations"," before"," and"," after"," class"," imb","ue"," students"," with"," a"," sense"," of"," community"," and"," belonging","."," These"," unplanned"," yet"," valuable"," encounters"," between"," students"," are"," conspicuously"," absent"," in"," the"," online"," classroom","."," The"," lack"," of"," physical"," presence"," can"," lead"," to"," feelings"," of"," isolation"," and"," detachment",","," st","unting"," the"," development"," of"," critical"," interpersonal"," skills"," and"," reducing"," opportunities"," for"," forming"," meaningful"," relationships",","," which"," are"," as"," much"," a"," part"," of"," education"," as"," academic"," learning",".","\n","Moreover",","," online"," classes"," often"," fail"," to"," provide"," effective"," one","-","on","-","one"," support"," from"," teachers","."," Physical"," cues"," and"," immediate"," verbal"," feedback"," that"," are"," crucial"," for"," instructional"," adaptation"," are"," lost"," in"," a"," virtual"," interface","."," Students"," struggling"," with"," material"," may"," find"," it"," difficult"," to"," communicate"," their"," issues"," during"," a"," video"," conference",","," where"," time"," is"," limited",","," and"," the"," environment"," is"," less"," personal","."," Consequently",","," students"," may"," forego"," seeking"," help"," altogether",","," leading"," to"," a"," downward"," spiral"," in"," their"," performance"," and"," confidence",".","\n","Lastly",","," the"," abundance"," of"," screen"," time"," associated"," with"," online"," learning"," cannot"," be"," overlooked","."," Excessive"," exposure"," to"," digital"," devices"," is"," linked"," to"," a"," plethora"," of"," health"," issues",","," including"," eye"," strain",","," poor"," posture",","," and"," disturbed"," sleep"," patterns","."," Furthermore",","," it"," contributes"," to"," a"," sedentary"," lifestyle"," that"," can"," have"," long","-","lasting"," negative"," effects"," on"," students","'"," physical"," well","-","being",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," convenience"," of"," online"," education"," cannot"," be"," disputed",","," it"," comes"," at"," a"," significant"," cost"," to"," the"," students","'"," social"," development",","," access"," to"," personalized"," teaching",","," and"," health"," due"," to"," increased"," screen"," time","."," Schools"," ought"," to"," carefully"," weigh"," these"," consequences"," and"," prioritize"," conventional"," in","-","person"," education"," that"," hol","istically"," nur","tures"," students","'"," academic"," and"," socio","-","emotional"," growth","."," In"," preparing"," young"," minds"," for"," the"," future",","," the"," value"," of"," direct"," human"," engagement"," should"," not"," be"," underestimated"," or"," sacrificed"," on"," the"," altar"," of"," technological"," advancement","."],"sub_source":"outfox","m